Local N4 deployment
===================

The N4 Compose deployment pulls LinuxServer.io container images for Radarr and
Sonarr at installation time. These images and applications are separate works;
they are not copied into the VynodeNew source tree or presented as VynodeNew UI.

Image documentation and source:
https://docs.linuxserver.io/images/docker-radarr/
https://github.com/linuxserver/docker-radarr
https://docs.linuxserver.io/images/docker-sonarr/
https://github.com/linuxserver/docker-sonarr

Application corresponding source:
https://github.com/Radarr/Radarr
https://github.com/Sonarr/Sonarr

Review the notices and licenses shipped inside each pulled image before
redistribution. VynodeNew retains this attribution while keeping upstream names,
logos, and interface assets out of the product interface.
